					<a href="#">Q. How to cancel membership/ delete my HANPASS account? <span class="faq-arrow"></span></a>
					<div class="news-toggle">
						<p class="news-text">
							To cancel you have to sign in in HANPASS app and click Settings -> Delete account. However, you cannot delete or cancel your membership in HANPASS if you have pending remittance request or transaction. Please also be guided that there will be limitation in terms of registering a bank account that you have previously registered under the HANPASS account that you have deleted.
